/before-the-kiss-gustav-klimt-got-his-first-big-art-assignment-at-this-austrian-theater-now-visitors-can-see-his-ceiling-paintings-up-close-for-the-first-time-180988698/</guid></item><item><title>FDA 批准的家用大脑刺激装置旨在通过改变患者大脑兴奋性来治疗抑郁症</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/fda-approved-at-home-brain-stimulation-device-aims-to-treat-depression-by-changing-patients-brain-excitability-180988654/</link><description>该治疗包括一个蓝牙耳机，患者可以将其连接到智能手机上的应用程序。它可能标志着精神健康医学的一场革命</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 16:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/fda-approved-at-home-brain-stimulation-device-aims-to-treat-depression-by-changing-patients-brain-excitability-180988654/</guid></item><item><title>巨大的海狮将人群吸引到旧金山著名的 39 号码头。然后，一个新的矮胖的表演者窃取了他的身份</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/chonkers-the-massive-sea-lion-drew-crowds-to-san-franciscos-famed-pier-39-then-a-new-chunky-showstopper-stole-his-identity-180988691/</link><description>北海狮是码头上的不寻常访客，码头上通常栖息着较小的加州海狮。然而，他可能在几天前​​就已经搬走了，在此期间，该地区较常见物种的一个巨大成员欺骗了旁观者</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 16:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/chonkers-the-massive-sea-lion-drew-crowds-to-san-franciscos-famed-pier-39-then-a-new-chunky-showstopper-stole-his-identity-180988691/</guid></item><item><title>城市鸟类似乎比男性更害怕女性——科学家们不知道为什么</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/urban-birds-seem-to-be-more-fearful-of-women-than-men-and-scientists-dont-know-why-180988688/</link><description>该研究调查了五个欧洲国家城市中的 37 种鸟类。在飞走之前，这些动物平均允许男性比女性靠近约三英尺</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/urban-birds-seem-to-be-more-fearful-of-women-than-men-and-scientists-dont-know-why-180988688/</guid></item><item><title>在成为国父之前，本杰明·富兰克林创立了借阅图书馆。现在，他的物品在拍卖前陈列在那里</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/before-benjamin-franklins-belongings-he